---
import Diagram from '../../../components/Diagram.astro';
import CodeBlock from '../../../components/CodeBlock.astro';
import MermaidDiagram from '../../../components/MermaidDiagram.astro';
import TreeView from '../../../components/TreeView.astro';
---

  <section class="component-group" id="group-diagrams">
    <header class="component-group__header">
      <h2>Diagram &amp; code</h2>
      <p>ASCII diagram, highlight code (Shiki), và ví dụ snippet.</p>
    </header>

  {/* ─────── Diagram ─────── */}
  <section class="showcase-section" id="diagram">
    <h3>Diagram</h3>
    <div class="example-render">
      <Diagram>
        <Fragment is:raw>
          ┌──────────┐     ┌──────────┐
          │  Model   │ ──▶ │  Tool    │
          └──────────┘     └──────────┘
          ▲                │
          └────── result ◀─┘
        </Fragment>
      </Diagram>
    </div>
    <pre class="example-code"><code>{`<Diagram><Fragment is:raw>...</Fragment></Diagram>`}</code></pre>
  </section>

  {/* ─────── CodeBlock ─────── */}
  <section class="showcase-section" id="codeblock">
    <h3>CodeBlock</h3>
    <div class="example-render">
      <CodeBlock caption="caption.ts">
        <Fragment is:raw>function hi(name) {
  return "hi " + name;
}</Fragment>
      </CodeBlock>
    </div>
    <p class="tip">
      <strong>Tip:</strong> highlight bằng <a href="https://shiki.style/">Shiki</a> (github-light /
      github-dark, theo <code>prefers-color-scheme</code>). Khi code có <code>{'{'}</code>/
      <code>{'}'}</code>, bọc slot bằng{" "}
      <code>{'<Fragment is:raw>...</Fragment>'}</code>.
      Prop tuỳ chọn <code>lang</code> (vd <code>typescript</code>, <code>bash</code>, <code>markdown</code>);
      không truyền thì component suy luận. Chuỗi HTML span cũ (<code>.kw</code>…) vẫn được strip và
      highlight lại.
    </p>
    <pre class="example-code"><code>{`<CodeBlock caption="loop.ts" lang="typescript">
  <Fragment is:raw>async function runLoop() { ... }</Fragment>
</CodeBlock>

<CodeBlock code="const x = 1;" lang="typescript" />`}</code></pre>
  </section>

  {/* ─────── MermaidDiagram ─────── */}
  <section class="showcase-section" id="mermaiddiagram">
    <h3>MermaidDiagram</h3>
    <p>Render Mermaid.js diagram từ CDN — tự detect dark/light theme. Hỗ trợ flowchart, sequence, gantt, ER. Dùng thay <code>Diagram</code> ASCII khi cần visual phức tạp hơn.</p>
    <div class="example-render">
      <MermaidDiagram
        chart={`graph TD
  A([User Request]) --> B{Agent Loop}
  B --> C[Call LLM]
  C --> D{Tool Call?}
  D -- yes --> E[Execute Tool]
  E --> F[Append Result]
  F --> B
  D -- no --> G([Return Response])`}
        caption="Agent loop decision flow"
      />
    </div>
    <pre class="example-code"><code>{`<MermaidDiagram
  chart={\`graph TD
    A[Request] --> B{Tool Call?}
    B -- yes --> C[Execute Tool]
    B -- no --> D[Return]\`}
  caption="Agent loop flow"
/>`}</code></pre>
  </section>

  {/* ─────── TreeView ─────── */}
  <section class="showcase-section" id="treeview">
    <h3>TreeView</h3>
    <p>File/directory tree với icon và màu theo extension. Thay thế <code>Diagram</code> ASCII cho folder structures.</p>
    <div class="example-render">
      <TreeView tree={`
tool/
  bash.ts  # implementation + schema
  bash.txt  # description template
  edit.ts
  edit.txt
  read.ts
src/
  agent/
    loop.ts
    session.ts
  context/
    compact.ts
    window.ts
  data/
    reports.ts
`} caption="Cấu trúc tool folder của opencode" />
    </div>
    <pre class="example-code"><code>{`<TreeView tree={\`
src/
  components/
    Button.astro
  pages/
    index.astro
\`} caption="Project structure" />`}</code></pre>
  </section>

  </section>
